@startuml diagrama de actividades MOCA

title MOCA

|User|
start
:Opens MOCA test card;
:Selects an option\nRegister / Modify / Consult;

if (Option selected?) then (Consult)
  |System|
  :Fetches and displays existing results;
  |User|
  :Exits;
  stop
else (Register or Modify)
  :Enters raw score and notes;
  |System|
  :Applies schooling bonus if applicable\n+2 if schooling <= 12 years and score <= 29;
  :Shows live final score and interpretation;
  |User|
  if (Wants to save?) then (yes)
    |System|
    :Saves results;
    stop
  else (no)
    :Exits;
    stop
  endif
endif

@enduml